A '''page droid''' was a model of [[Droid/Legends|droid]]. The [[Human-Qieg Guild]] that governed the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Lan Barell/Legends|Lan Barell]] utilized page droids inside the [[Quilan Hive]] as guides to assist visitors in navigating the labyrinthine interior. They were available for the price of a few [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]].<ref name="LB">{{JournalCite|1|Lan Barell (article)}}</ref> The [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] employed page droids to carry out errands within the [[New Republic Senate/Legends|New Republic Senate's]] [[Grand Convocation Chamber]].<ref name="HT">''[[The New Jedi Order: Agents of Chaos I: Hero's Trial]]''</ref>

